Author: etheal_dev
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Dev update: https://medium.com/etheal/etheal-dev-roadmap-behring-update-b5de4edc6700  We broke down our development roadmap into 4 parts, and have been working full steam ahead on implementing Etheal‚Ää‚Äî‚Äänow we‚Äôre proud to announce that we have checked off phase one, the Behring release, one month early!  Etheal‚Äôs Development Roadmap Behring Release. The goal: To reach and grow profitability ‚úîÔ∏èDONE Sir Ronald Ross Release. The goal: To grow traffic. Finsen Release. The goal: To grow conversion. Pavlov Release. The goal: To expand to 30 countries.  Dev updates from the Behring release: We translated the Etheal platform into 5 new languages: Russian, German, English, Italian, French! 40,000 doctors and 88,000 services are indexed in every language and available to the international community Our Pareto Revenue infrastructure is live We have begun signing up paying partners who are actively using the site Crypto integration for clinics has been added: membership and leads can be purchased with HEAL tokens and additional cryptocurrencies   Implementing the Sir Ronald Ross release one month early: Our number one goal: to scale the adoption of Etheal and grow traffic.  By focusing on this goal for the next quarter, we will simultaneously be solving the problems of our users, and profiting our partners, doctors and clinics worldwide, while also working to reach profitability.  About Sir Ronald Ross Sir Ronald Ross, a British medical doctor from British India, received the Nobel Prize in Medicine for his work on the transmission of malaria, and was the first Nobel laureate born outside of Europe.  He realized and proved that malaria was transmitted by mosquitos, which laid the foundation for preventing the spread of the disease.   Sir Ronald Ross worked in the Indian Medical Service for 25 years, where he made his most famous discovery.  Besides his exceptional work in the field of medicine, he was also a polymath. He wrote a number of poems, published books and songs and was also a passionate amateur artist. His work and life as a true renaissance man is inspiring for our team and mission, as we build a solution that combines a number of different fields.  Q4 2018: The Sir Ronald Ross release Etheal‚Äôs infrastructure is ready for worldwide adoption, and throughout this and the next releases our main focus is to grow traffic, reach patients globally, and bring clients to our partner clinics.  Upcoming Features: Optimize our current architecture, including CDN and sitespeed Begin expanding to 30 different countries, a module that we have brought forward from our planned Q2 2019 Pavlov Release Refactor the codebase Build a database within the new countries that we expand to Partner with new clinics and doctors in target countries Deploy the 360 review integration for doctors and clinics Timeline: We are moving faster than planned, which means we are beginning our next release one month ahead of schedule.  We‚Äôve moved up significant expansion modules from our final planned Pavlov release, in order to accelerate Etheal‚Äôs mainstream adoption and take advantage of our rapid implementation.  Our deadline for the implementation of the expanded Sir Ronald Ross release is Q4 2018.

Author: peterkate630
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: About Etheal The Etheal Trust Score (ETS) will reflect the general reliability of a wallet address. The score is a combination of factors, including how early and well a specific wallet address upvotes important and popular content and how much HEAL token the address owns.  The idea for ETS is based on the ‚Äúbelievability score‚Äù from Bridgewater Associates - the biggest and most successful hedge fund in the world. Compared to a democracy where the majority decides, or autocracy where a selected minority decides, the believability score fosters idea meritocracy by weighing the votes of how believable the voter is [41]. ETS will be used to weigh upvotes when calculating stakes for the Weekly Contribution Endowment Fund.  The Etheal Rank Score (ERS) will reflect how much total value a user has generated in the ecosystem by, for example, writing useful content, showing up for appointments in time, or getting good reviews. The Etheal Rank will determine what special features an account has access to, like moderating disputes. Each transaction will be recorded in the blockchain with the address of the service provider and user, and encrypted details of the transaction. Both parties can write a review based on each transaction, and open a dispute when necessary. Resolving disputes without external intervention will be incentivized, but when necessary the issue will automatically be forwarded to a committee of moderators. Etheal Trust and Etheal Rank scores of all participants are updated automatically.  Care providers will be able to embed their reviews easily to their personal website with a dedicated review widget and API.

Author: etheal_dev
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: üî•We have good news for you! The date of token sale is FINAL!üî•    We are going to close the whitelist deposit period on June 18. The token sale will open on June 25 and it will last for maximum 4 weeks.  The dates are changed compared to what we originally planned, because we got an overwhelming interest from all around the world! We got invited to an outstanding number of conferences, meetups and workshops and we happily accepted these invitations, because we had the chance to promote Etheal on 3 continents on 25+ events and build a truly international community.   We were focusing on forming key partnerships:  1. Meetups, workshops, conferences: we went to 3 continents to 25+ conferences: https://etheal.com/#events  2. IEEE (the biggest IT organization, developing standards like 5G): we are part of a small and dedicated team to create a standard around scoring and managing private medical data on blockchain. In the short term we focus on building a public global medical platform (to minimize our legal risks regarding our global expansion), in the future we will incorporate private medical data as well in our system.  3. IDACB (International Decentralized Association of Cryptocurrency and Blockchain): we got invited and accepted the role to be part of the board of directors at the biggest decentralized association around blockchain  4. Hong Kong Blockchain Society invited our CTO and co-founder Viktor as an international observer, and Viktor got also invited to hold a smart contract security workshop at the Hong Kong Polytechnic University.  5. Viktor also gave a workshop about secure smart contract development at the University of California Irvine  6. Viktor will also network next week with top healthcare leaders at the highly selective Stanford University Innovative Healthcare Leader Executive Education program.  7. The Finance Minister (2009-2010) of Hungary joined Etheal as an advisor: https://medium.com/etheal/etheal-advisory-board-peter-oszko-7d0d05d4c5ac   What we are working on until the token sale:  1. Proper PR with a top notch London based PR agency, who is the European partner of Houbi and helped one of the most successful Slovenian ICOs  2. Meetups in three cities: Seoul, Beijng and Budapest  3. Having a smart contract development workshop and meetup in the University of Beijing (with the tremendous help from one of our strategic investor, we got an official approval from the local authorities, which is very rare for blockchain projects in China)  4. Publishing the demo website. Currently the working website Doklist.com is in Hungarian and in Portuguese only and it‚Äôs harder to understand its benefits for English speaker community  5. Updated website based on the new pitch deck and the 100+ feedback that our community gave is in the last week in the questionnaires.  6. We are planning to reach more people with paid media on Etherscan, Icobench (where we already have an outstanding rating), Coinmarketcap, Whattomine.com, Walletinvestor and several other ICO listing sites and cryptocurrency related forums.  7. Closing the deals with strategic partners from 3 continents with the best conditions.  8. Airdropping 900 (911 to be exact) ‚ÄúHEALP‚Äù promo tokens to 2,000,000 ethereum addresses, which can be used by everyone to get +5% bonus.  We would like to reinforce, that we have noted that our communication wasn‚Äôt clear regarding the whitelist period, so we are granting +5% bonus to compensate the inconvenience of all the 98 contributors who have sent their contributions during the first hour on April 9, when we opened the token sale.  We updated our pitch deck and we would appreciate your detailed feedback. Pitch deck: http://bit.ly/EthealPitchDeck Feedback form: https://etheal.typeform.com/to/dwNiQR  Kind regards, Dr. Mihaly Kertesz CEO, Etheal

Author: etheal_dev
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Our main competitors are centralized doctor listing sites (ZocDoc, Doctoralia). The biggests problems with these services: (a) You can only compare doctors. While we compare physicians by treatments and not just specialty. It is important because, if your wife is endangered pregnant with twins, you won‚Äôt look for any gynecologist, you will look for the best gynecologist who has deep expertise with endangered twin pregnancies. There are 44.000 listed services on our site, while our competitors has no more than 1000 listed services. Our live websites: doklist.com and doklist.com.br For more details see 5.3.1 in Whitepaper http://etheal.com/etheal-wp-0.8.pdf  (b) Our competitors don‚Äôt incetivize patients to write reviews. We‚Äôll incentivize them with the Weekly Contribution Endowment Funds, so they can earn HEAL tokens, if they contribute. See 5.3.3.5 in whitepaper.  (c) If a doctor stops paying for our competitors‚Äô monthly listing fees (which is $300/doctors at ZocDoc), all his reviews are gone. We provide transferable reviews handled by smart contracts and blockchain. So a doctor won‚Äôt ever loose his hard-earned reviews. See 5.3.2.1 in Whitepaper for more details http://etheal.com/etheal-wp-0.8.pdf

Author: etheal_cm
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: HODL reward means, that you participate in pre-sale or normal sale, and you leave all your HEAL tokens untouched,then after 3 months of normal sale we distribute 1M HEAL tokens among those who HODL (didn't touch any portion of their funds), after 6 months we distribute an additional 2M HEAL tokens and after 9 months we distribute 7M more HEAL tokens, so you are incentivized to hold all your tokens for 9 months. For example if you move some or all of your funds at 7 months after normal sale, then you will get a portion of 3 months hodl reward (1M token), and 6 months hodl reward (2M token) if you keep all funds untouched for 9 months after normal sale, then you get a portion of all 3 hodl reward rounds.

Author: spartasparta007
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Etheal (HEAL)- Airdrop - Bonuties #1 About Etheal The Etheal Trust Score (ETS) will reflect the general reliability of a wallet address. The score is a combination of factors, including how early and well a specific wallet address upvotes important and popular content and how much HEAL token the address owns.  The idea for ETS is based on the ‚Äúbelievability score‚Äù from Bridgewater Associates - the biggest and most successful hedge fund in the world. Compared to a democracy where the majority decides, or autocracy where a selected minority decides, the believability score fosters idea meritocracy by weighing the votes of how believable the voter is [41]. ETS will be used to weigh upvotes when calculating stakes for the Weekly Contribution Endowment Fund.  The Etheal Rank Score (ERS) will reflect how much total value a user has generated in the ecosystem by, for example, writing useful content, showing up for appointments in time, or getting good reviews. The Etheal Rank will determine what special features an account has access to, like moderating disputes. Each transaction will be recorded in the blockchain with the address of the service provider and user, and encrypted details of the transaction. Both parties can write a review based on each transaction, and open a dispute when necessary. Resolving disputes without external intervention will be incentivized, but when necessary the issue will automatically be forwarded to a committee of moderators. Etheal Trust and Etheal Rank scores of all participants are updated automatically.

Author: etheal_support
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Hey, thanks for your question.  We are not just a Yelp-like doctor listing site. We have already categorized 88.000 medical services, while our competitors have listed less than 100 medical services.  Making medical treatments searchable is a tedious task since there are no ISBN codes and no industry standard XML feeds to easily process large amounts of offers from a large number of physicians. We had to build on our experience, and use a great deal of Natural Language Processing to make more than 40,000 physicians searchable by more than 88,000 medical services in Hungary. This was a huge jump in data compared to the databases of our international competitors.  You might ask what‚Äôs the benefit of 88.000 medical services:  If you or your partner is endangered pregnant with twins, you won‚Äôt settle for just any gynecologist; you will want a highly recommended gynecologist with  deep expertise in managing endangered pregnancies with twins.  So you don‚Äôt want a general Yelp-like review of a doctor, but you want a review of the physician‚Äôs services.  See more 5.1.1 in our whitepaper: https://etheal.com/etheal-wp.pdf

Author: etheal_support
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Thank you for your question. Etheal is not just a Yelp-like doctor listing site. We have already categorized 88.000 medical services, while our competitors have listed less than 100 medical services.  Making medical treatments searchable is a tedious task since there are no ISBN codes and no industry standard XML feeds to easily process large amounts of offers from a large number of physicians. We had to build on our experience, and use a great deal of Natural Language Processing to make more than 40,000 physicians searchable by more than 88,000 medical services in Hungary. This was a huge jump in data compared to the databases of our international competitors.  You might ask what‚Äôs the benefit of 88.000 medical services:  If you or your partner is endangered pregnant with twins, you won‚Äôt settle for just any gynecologist; you will want a highly recommended gynecologist with  deep expertise in managing endangered pregnancies with twins.  So you don‚Äôt want a general Yelp-like review of a doctor, but you want a review of the physician‚Äôs services.  See more 5.1.1 in our whitepaper: https://etheal.com/etheal-wp.pdf

Author: etheal_support
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Hi elenJdy!  Patientory want to solve a very important problem by placing private health records on the blockchain while maintaining the privacy of the information. We are focusing on incentivizing and decentralizing public medical data.  Patientory helps care providers to store private medical data into blockchain AFTER patients obtain care, we solve a more fundamental problem to find care in the first place with a Steemit-like incentivized content platform for care providers and booking platform for patients. Author: etheal_support
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Hey! Our thinking was that moving the reviews to blockchain eliminates the problem that a traditional centralized competitor (e.g. what Zocdoc) creates. A doctor builds his reputation in the platform over a period. But if he stops paying the subscription fees, for his/her profile, the all the work over the time span is lost. All the reviews from the patients are gone in the wind. S/he basically gets tightly integrated with the centralized system. With the use of blockchain, the reviews and scores remain forever and no one can change, remove or manipulate it.

Body: Hey! Thanks for your question. Patientory want to solve a very important problem by placing private health records on the blockchain while maintaining the privacy of the information. We are focusing on incentivizing and decentralizing public medical data.  Patientory helps care providers to store private medical data into blockchain AFTER patients obtain care, we solve a more fundamental problem to find care in the first place with a Steemit-like incentivized content platform for care providers and booking platform for patients. We don't help care providers privately to store medical info, but help patients to find trusted care providers around the globe.

Body: Hey there! Until the soft-cap is reached, normal sale price will be 1ETH=1000 HEAL token. If you buy during presale, you get 25% bonus!

Author: etheal_support
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Hey! Thank you for your question. Our thinking was that moving the reviews to blockchain eliminates the problem that a traditional centralized competitor (e.g. what Zocdoc) creates. A doctor builds his reputation in the platform over a period. But if he stops paying the subscription fees, for his/her profile, the all the work over the time span is lost. All the reviews from the patients are gone in the wind. S/he basically gets tightly integrated with the centralized system. With the use of blockchain, the reviews and scores remain forever and no one can change, remove or manipulate it.

Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Hey! I am glad you asked. Patientory wants to solve a very important problem by placing private health records on the blockchain while maintaining the privacy of the information. We are focusing on incentivizing and decentralizing public medical data.  Patientory helps care providers to store private medical data into blockchain AFTER patients obtain care, we solve a more fundamental problem to find care in the first place with a Steemit-like incentivized content platform for care providers and booking platform for patients. We don't help care providers privately to store medical info, but help patients to find trusted care providers around the globe.

Author: etheal_support
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Hey, nice question. However, we are not just a Yelp-like doctor listing site. We have already categorized 88.000 medical services, while our competitors have listed less than 100 medical services.  Making medical treatments searchable is a tedious task since there are no ISBN codes and no industry standard XML feeds to easily process large amounts of offers from a large number of physicians. We had to build on our experience, and use a great deal of Natural Language Processing to make more than 40,000 physicians searchable by more than 88,000 medical services in Hungary. This was a huge jump in data compared to the databases of our international competitors.  You might ask what‚Äôs the benefit of 88.000 medical services:  If you or your partner is endangered pregnant with twins, you won‚Äôt settle for just any gynecologist; you will want a highly recommended gynecologist with  deep expertise in managing endangered pregnancies with twins.  So you don‚Äôt want a general Yelp-like review of a doctor, but you want a review of the physician‚Äôs services.  See more 5.1.1 in our whitepaper: https://etheal.com/etheal-wp.pdf

Body: Hey! Good question, but no, we are not just a Yelp-like doctor listing site. We have already categorized 88.000 medical services, while our competitors have listed less than 100 medical services.  Making medical treatments searchable is a tedious task since there are no ISBN codes and no industry standard XML feeds to easily process large amounts of offers from a large number of physicians. We had to build on our experience, and use a great deal of Natural Language Processing to make more than 40,000 physicians searchable by more than 88,000 medical services in Hungary. This was a huge jump in data compared to the databases of our international competitors.  You might ask what‚Äôs the benefit of 88.000 medical services:  If you or your partner is endangered pregnant with twins, you won‚Äôt settle for just any gynecologist; you will want a highly recommended gynecologist with  deep expertise in managing endangered pregnancies with twins.  So you don‚Äôt want a general Yelp-like review of a doctor, but you want a review of the physician‚Äôs services.  See more 5.1.1 in our whitepaper: https://etheal.com/etheal-wp.pdf

Author: etheal_dev
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Hi baselhund, We admire Patientory as they want to solve a very important problem: to put PRIVATE medical data (health records) on the blockchain while maintaining privacy.  We are focusing on incentivizing and decentralizing PUBLIC medical data (reviews, recommendations, articles from medical professionals).  Patientory helps care providers to store private medical data into blockchain AFTER patients obtain care, we solve a more fundamental problem to find care in the first place with a Steemit-like incentivized content platform for care providers and booking platform for patients.  We don't help care providers privately to store medical info, but help patients to find trusted care providers around the globe.

There will be individual caps for whitelist contribution period, so everyone on the whitelist has a guaranteed spot on the first day. 15 ETH individual cap on Nov 29th 65 ETH individual cap on Nov 30th  There will be no individual cap on the open crowdsale. Author: etheal_dev
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Yes, that's right, we can confirm it.  We are not competitors with Patientory.  We admire Patientory as they want to solve a very important problem: to put PRIVATE medical data (health records) on the blockchain while maintaining privacy.  We are focusing on incentivizing and decentralizing PUBLIC medical data (reviews, recommendations, articles from medical professionals).  Patientory helps care providers to store private medical data into blockchain AFTER patients obtain care, we solve a more fundamental problem to find care in the first place with a Steemit-like incentivized content platform for care providers and booking platform for patients.  We don't help care providers privately to store medical info, but help patients to find trusted care providers around the globe.  Maybe we can have a partnership with Patientory in the future.

Author: etheal_dev
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: Thank you beginneraf for your perspective and your kind support, and thank you olcaytu2005 for the question.  Under traditional settings it would be very hard to micro incentivize people, regardless of physical borders (mainly because of transaction fees and there are places where getting a bank account or credit card is not as easy as in western developed countries). Setting up an ethereum address takes a few seconds, compare that to how much time it takes to get a bank account or credit card.  So with smart contracts and blockchain, we can create a layer on which we can scale. So with this awesome community and a unified blockchain settlement layer we can scale and increase our current 2.5 million visits per year by expanding to more countries without limit.  Since blockchain enables micro incentivization, we can create superb quality local databases 10x better than current solutions (similarly how Steemit rapidly grew to 16.5M monthly visits by incentivizing good content creation) , which enables us to become a dominant player in the medical tourism market, which is projected to grow to $540 billion by 2025 by Oxford Economics and Visa.  There are other aspects as well, like a traditional centralized player - ZocDoc - has raised $223 million from Venture Capitalists, and they charge $300 per month per doctor, to collect reviews and provide an online profile for physicians. When a doctor stops paying, she looses all her reviews, since ZocDoc owns all the reviews.  We deeply believe in a future where healthcare is global, inclusive and not dominated by any central player. This is why we aim to build a decentralized blockchain-based healthcare platform, and ultimately improving the lives of 1 billion people. Currently we potentially reach 230 million people in Brazil and Hungary, so having a positive impact on 1 billion people is not out of sight.  I am aware that this topic is complex, which is partly a reason why there are not too many healthcare projects, and this is why we are focusing on building a multi-disciplinary team.  For further details, please see Section 5.2 of our Whitepaper, or feel free to ask any question.

Author: Kooream
Title: ‚ù§Ô∏èETHEAL‚ù§Ô∏èBringing transparency to $100bn+ medical tourism [30% BONUS period]‚ù§Ô∏è
Body: https://i.imgur.com/VdP09Qo.png  Bring transparency to $100+ BillionMedical Tourism  Improving the lives of 1 billion people by making Healthcare more transparent  ‚≠êÔ∏è TOP-RATED ICO: ICObench 4.5/5, ICOmarks 9.0/10 Track  ICO 5/5 üèÜ Award winning concept: CES Blockchain competition 2nd, d10e Audience AwardüèÜ  Etheal.com Videos Whitepaper Lightpaper Smart Contract Telegram  Current state We are currently focused on migrating our working healthcare service comparison portal to the blockchain. 141,858 lines of code 2.5+ million visits per year 420,000 care providers Brazil - Doklist.com.br Hungary - Doklist.com  https://i.imgur.com/IPPbVBc.png https://i.imgur.com/8qNc88K.pnghttps://i.imgur.com/yb70yTM.png  https://i.imgur.com/tM85VvG.png https://i.imgur.com/Ed5QDHK.png  https://i.imgur.com/sjR83Nd.png  Opportunity Healthcare expenditure grows by $300B every year. https://i.imgur.com/0jn7lkK.png Source: Deloitte.  Healthcare is 10x bigger than global hotel industry Priceline Group (Booking.com) made $10.64 billion last year in revenue, by selling accommodations online. Their current share price is above $1,800.  According to Oxford Economics and Visa, medical tourism is predicted to become a $540 billion industry by 2025 with 25% CAGR. https://i.imgur.com/n4hOCuX.png   Problem Healthcare is fundamentally broken.     Unnecessary deaths to inefficiencies  Increased participation in colon cancer screenings alone could lead to 21,000 saved lives every year in the US alone.  source: Kennedy Health Alliance   Our solution We build on top of giants, who have laid down current solutions (blockchain, crypto assets, smart contracts, etc.) We intensely focus on UX and hiding the complexity of crypto world, creating a gateway for a vast amount of users and money to join the biggest revolution since widespread internet adoption. We have already tested our strategy, 2,500,000 people use our site yearly (Doklist.com), and we currently potentially reach 230M people on 2 opposing sides of the world (Brazil and Hungary).  Our goal is to build a 2.0 decentralized version of our current successful solution, which is based on 141 858 lines of code and serves 2.5M visits a year. We have planned every step of our roadmap to maximize the value increase of the Etheal ecosystem in the shortest amount of time possible.  First, we are focused on creating a decentralized incentivization and unified settlement layer in Ethereum. This will help us rapidly expand to 30 countries and increase the quality of our local doctor databases with automated smart contract driven incentives.  Taking advantage of the blockchain-based incentive system and the resulting high-quality global database, we aim to quickly become a dominant player in rapidly growing markets (medical tourism and pharmaceutical communication research and advertisement), currently worth more than $117 billion globally.  Opening up our platform to let anyone write an Etheal Application is the logical next step to grow the Etheal Ecosystem further.  Finally, we will focus on the maintenance, development, and marketing of the Etheal platform for it to become the ‚ÄúBooking.com, Steemit and Salesforce of Healthcare‚Äù, with a model capable of generating $100B+ of potential revenue.  Selling the proper utility HEAL token is the next step on our roadmap. You can now join our community and help us build a better healthcare system together.  https://i.imgur.com/Iirj1o6.jpg    Business Model The strongest short-term growth driver will be Medical Tourism lead generation, where the market is predicted to grow to $540 billion by 2025 according to Oxford Economics and Visa.  The second biggest growth driver will be pharmaceutical communication research and advertisement, which is a $27 billion market in the USA alone.  Physicians will also be able to bid to be included in the top 3 featured spots on search results, where in contrast to Google Adwords, their quality score is not dependent on how good of a website they have, but instead on the quality of service they provide. A doctor who provides excellent service, will have to pay less for the same featured spot.  5% of all revenue generated through the Etheal Ecosystem will go to the Etheal Operation Fund to cover operating expenses, 15% will go to the Weekly Contribution Endowment Fund rewarding patients and care providers.  Most of the applications developed by us will be free, however, paid applications will use different models. For instance, pharmaceutical advertising is planned to be a revenue share model of 70%-30%, where users earn 70% and 30% goes to the Etheal Operation Fund.   Ecosystem https://i.imgur.com/rzIhc6T.png  Decentralization Layer: used to store permanent information in the blockchain and to transparently automate incentivization and the payment layer of the ecosystem while storing larger quantities of data on the InterPlanetary File System (IPFS).  Backend Off-chain Layer: used to cache and hold data and changes which are not needed to be stored in the blockchain and to provide an API endpoint to easily access and embed data from the ecosystem in any website or application.  Etheal Platform Layer: consists of a sandbox and a simplified UX and mobile-friendly front-end where stakeholders can interact with the Etheal Ecosystem.   Why blockchain? With the blockchain, we can instantly resolve our most difficult scaling and automation challenges.  Charlie Munger says that getting incentives right is the most fundamental thing to build a sustainable business.  Incentivization Solution: easy to reward ecosystem contributors Cross border: time tested way of move value regardless of physical borders Micropayments: quick and cheap Fully automated, transparent contracts: a layer we can scale-on, and it works magically, transparently and verifiably   Why do we need a dedicated token? An internal token which can be used as a dedicated method to get discounted services, and transfer value. Fair initial distribution, and balanced long-term incentives to reward those, who use and contribute to the ecosystem. To build a community, which believes in a future of better healthcare.  What is the use of HEAL tokens? Internal payment for services Cross border payment for medical services Community incentivized for moving the ecosystem forward Buying research participation and advertisement by big-pharma companies  What does Etheal plan to do to grow demand for HEAL token? We will hide the complexity of buying a crypto token by planning our proprietary fiat-·∏™ exchange (in which our team has experience) We also make it trivial for new users to buy tokens and services with current exchange partners The more people use ETHEAL, the higher the demand is projected to grow. The more countries we expand to, the higher the demand is projected to grow. The more applications are built on top of the ecosystem, the higher the demand is projected to grow.  Token vesting Founders and team members are fully vested for 3 years (with a one year cliff) Advisors are vested for 6 months (with a three month cliff)  Ecosystem incentives Incentivize developers in 10 strategic areas according to the usage of their applications in the ecosystem. We optimize to create a review system which is useful across borders (geography aware). In the last decade, we have worked in the cut-throat competitive e-commerce field, where we gained invaluable experience.  Use of proceeds of token sale Intended to use for paying development bills, data processing, legal counselings, customer service, sales, marketing and in general to grow the ecosystem.   Main Sale Whitelist deposit period opens: April 9th, 2018 at 10:00AM GMT Tokens sold: 12,000,000 HEAL Duration: max 4 weeks Min contribution: 0.1 ETH Soft cap: 4.8M USD Base token price: 1 ETH = 600 ·∏™ token Hard cap: 10M USD reaching the hard cap ends the sale immediately All HEAL tokens are frozen until we distribute all main sale tokens Token sale bonus: https://etheal.com/img/chart-token-sale-bonus.svg Your stake = sum(bonusi x your transferi) We calculate your stake by summarizing all of your transfers increased by a bonus at the time of receiving the fund. Your tokens = 20,000,000·∏™ x sum(bonusi x your transferi) / sum(bonusj x transferj) At the end of the sale you will receive HEAL tokens, the amount of which is based on the ratio of your stake to the total stakes.   Referral Reward We have set aside 2M HEAL tokens to award those, who help to build the Etheal community in its early days.  Every whitelist applicant will get a personalized referral link, and they will get 5% bonus after every contribution using that link, plus each contributor will also get an additional 1% bonus for using a referral link.  Example: One of your friends signs up for whitelist using your referral link, and buys 10,000 HEAL tokens during sale. You will get an additional 7% * 10,000 = 700 HEAL tokens. Your friend will get 3% * 10,000 = 300 bonus HEAL tokens.  Remaining referral reward HEAL tokens will go to the HODLER reward fund (50% to lot 6 months and 50% to lot 9 months).   HODLER Reward To keep prices stable in the early months we use extensive vesting for founders, team and advisors, and we reward those who HODL.  Keep tokens intact (can‚Äôt move any portion of it) on your wallet for 3/6/9 months after the normal sale has ended, and a 10M HEAL token HODLER reward will be distributed in total among token sale HODLERs in the ratio of their intact stakes to the total amount.  HODLER lot 3 months: 1,000,000 HEAL HODLER lot 6 months: 2,000,000 HEAL HODLER lot 9 months: 17,000,000 HEAL   More information Whitepaper Website: etheal.com   Join us on discord or telegram.  Follow us / Contacts   Ask us directly on our telegram group: Telegram ENG Telegram ‰∏≠Êñá (China) Telegram Êó•Êú¨Ë™û (Japanese) Telegram ÌïúÍµ≠Ïñ¥ (Korea) Discord Twitter Facebook Youtube Medium Kakaotalk  Please note, that we are not looking for greedy whales and speculators seeking a quick P-n-D. We are obsessed to create value for the community of dedicated true believers in a new standard of healthcare (see the token vesting section).  Regards, Dr. Mihaly Kertesz Co-founder, COO (Linkedin) Viktor Tabori Co-founder, CTO (Linkedin)  Disclaimer: This ANN is not for US residents, US residents will not be able to participate in HEAL token sale.  Disclaimer: I'm not a project team member or anyhow related with this project. All responsibility belongs to the project‚Äôs team members.  Moderator: etheal_dev
